Tanchem kacheri sodunk proytan korop ek khoreponni bhonvddi!
Tanchi website sangta ki ti "B-27, Ansal Plaza, August Kranti Marg, New Delhi, 110049" hanga asa, punn khoreponnim, Ansal Plaza mhollear chodd chai pielolea eka monxan toyar kelolea gaddol sarko asa.
Hanv shapath ghetam, hanv "Dukan No. 14" sa suttim pasun gelem.
Google Maps mhakay parking-chea attendanthancho booth sarko dispi koddem vhelem.
Bari asa ki tankam aplo pot'to "Barista-lagim kuthtori, punn to sodunk dev bori khoro" oso noven korcho poddtto. ЁЯШВ
